### Get KPI by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/kpis/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get KPI not found (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/kpis/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get KPIs by Goal
GET http://localhost:8080/api/kpis/goal/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

